any closer to a consensus?

19:47.266 --> 19:49.333 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

19:49.333 --> 19:51.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JON TESTER: I don't know that
that's the kind of reform that
we need in our health care

19:51.633 --> 19:53.700 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
system.

19:53.700 --> 19:56.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think it may be more of
