And that's my concern.

20:03.433 --> 20:08.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, you don't
think that that version, which
some Republicans are saying

20:10.000 --> 20:13.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
would make them happy, bring
