20:15.500 --> 20:17.000 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

20:17.000 --> 20:18.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JON TESTER: Look, I don't think
it's going the move the ball.

20:18.233 --> 20:20.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
