the direction I want to go.

20:42.466 --> 20:44.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think that that skinny
bill, that bait-and-switch
bill, whatever you
want to call it, Trojan

20:44.766 --> 20:49.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
horse repeal bill, that bill
is not where we will end up at.

20:51.266 --> 20:53.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I don't think you get the
conservatives with that bill.

20:53.766 --> 20:56.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I don't think you
get the moderates either.

20:56.266 --> 21:00.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I think what's
happened here is, you
have got Mitch McConnell,
who has his vote today

21:00.633 --> 21:05.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
