21:05.033 --> 21:07.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to put it up to be able to
change the bill in conference.

21:07.800 --> 21:11.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's all very convoluted,
in the weeds, but that's
where we're headed.

21:11.300 --> 21:15.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Senator, you
mentioned Medicaid expansion
in your own state of Montana.

21:15.066 --> 21:20.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
