21:24.366 --> 21:28.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A number of people in
your state worrying this
program can't be sustained.

21:28.000 --> 21:31.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I guess they were expecting
maybe 30,000 to sign up.

21:31.400 --> 21:33.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
