about priorities.

21:56.400 --> 22:01.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And if our priority is to make
sure that people have access
to affordable health care, then

22:04.433 --> 22:06.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
we need to move forward.

22:06.533 --> 22:10.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
But we have got 77,000
