Medicaid expansion in
the state of a million

22:10.366 --> 22:12.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and 50,000 people.

22:12.100 --> 22:14.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I don't think that's
