small businesses that healthier,

22:23.633 --> 22:25.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
and I think it's an
important step to take.

22:25.033 --> 22:28.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But I think it's
about priorities.

22:28.200 --> 22:30.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We need to make health care
a priority in this country.

22:30.666 --> 22:35.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Democratic
Senator Jon Tester of Montana,
we thank you very much.

22:36.333 --> 22:38.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

22:38.066 --> 22:43.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JON TESTER: Thank you.

22:45.033 --> 22:49.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The escalation
of President Trump's criticism
of Jeff Sessions exposes

22:52.033 --> 22:57.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a rare public divide between
an American president
and his attorney general.

22:57.800 --> 22:59.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Jeffrey Brown reports.

22:59.800 --> 23:03.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of the
United States: I'm disappointed
in the attorney general.

23:04.466 --> 23:06.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He shouldn't have
recused himself.

23:06.466 --> 23:09.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: The
president's latest salvo
came this afternoon,
at his news conference

23:09.900 --> 23:11.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
with Lebanon's prime minister.

23:11.966 --> 23:16.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
