going to take you.

24:33.633 --> 24:38.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
It's extremely unfair,
and that's a mild
word, to the president.

24:38.133 --> 24:41.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: The next
day, Sessions said he
has no plans to resign.

24:41.733 --> 24:43.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFF SESSIONS: We love this job.

24:43.533 --> 24:45.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We love this department.

24:45.066 --> 24:48.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I plan to continue to do so
as long as that is appropriate.

24:48.833 --> 24:53.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The attorney
general has not been heard from
since, but several Republican

24:55.033 --> 24:57.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
