25:05.066 --> 25:08.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And Utah's Orrin Hatch
said he was surprised.

25:08.300 --> 25:10.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

25:10.366 --> 25:12.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
ORRIN HATCH (R), Utah:
Jeff has been very loyal
to the president, and
I think he deserves

25:12.933 --> 25:14.900 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
loyalty back.

25:14.900 --> 25:17.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Democrats warned
that forcing out Sessions
would spark a new firestorm.

25:17.800 --> 25:19.900 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

25:19.900 --> 25:21.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHUCK SCHUMER (D-NY), Minority
Leader: Many Americans must
be wondering if the president

25:21.966 --> 25:26.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
