Robert Mueller as the
special counsel and

27:11.833 --> 27:15.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
this investigation that
is dogging him still.

27:15.033 --> 27:20.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
