27:24.966 --> 27:29.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So it's clear he is still very
frustrated, very, in his words,
disappointed in his attorney

27:30.800 --> 27:33.333 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
general.

27:33.333 --> 27:35.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And,
