anything more coming out
of the Justice Department?

27:35.366 --> 27:38.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Do we know how the attorney
general is taking all this?

27:38.366 --> 27:41.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SARI HORWITZ, The Washington
Post: Well, you know, it's just
been an extraordinary spectacle

27:41.833 --> 27:43.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
playing out here in Washington.

27:43.866 --> 27:48.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
