Department he's been doing since
he got in as attorney general

28:17.900 --> 28:19.900 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in February.

28:19.900 --> 28:21.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You know, he recused himself
in March, and this has
been going on since March.

28:21.933 --> 28:26.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Sari, you and
