29:04.700 --> 29:09.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Like, if the states seem to be
harboring illegal immigrants,
undocumented immigrants, they

29:10.566 --> 29:12.600 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
