29:12.600 --> 29:16.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And what we're hearing is,
tomorrow or the next day, he's
going to be announcing that

29:16.566 --> 29:19.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the Justice Department is indeed
doing leak investigations.

29:19.700 --> 29:24.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: John, what do
you make of the support that
has been ever more vocal today,

29:26.133 --> 29:28.166 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
in fact, for Jeff Sessions
from friends and allies?

29:28.166 --> 29:32.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Well, I think,
Jeff, it really is one of the
