For the "PBS NewsHour,"
I'm Ken Christensen in
Seattle, Washington.

54:53.333 --> 54:54.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Very cool.

54:54.933 --> 54:56.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And that is the
"NewsHour" tonight.

54:56.400 --> 54:57.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I'm Judy Woodruff.

